  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial will be comparing the combination of amiodarone and NAC (n=122) to amiodarone
      alone and NAC matched placebo (n=122) to determine the rates with which sustained (lasting
      &gt;30 seconds) or clinically significant POAF is reduced in high risk patients within 7 days
      after major thoracic surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
